HTML-4:

italic:<i></i>tag,
bold:<b></b>tag.
text underline korte:<u></u>

HTML-5:
italic:<em></em> tag.
bold:<strong></strong> tag.
Text Highlight: <mark></mark> tag.
text choto korte: <small></small>
text  delete korte:<del></del> or <strick></strick>
text underline korte:<ins></ins>
Text ke blog o quotesion akare likhte:<blockquote></blockquote>
short quotesion er jonno:<q></q>
kew jokon kono abbreviation e click kore tar full form dekhabe emon korte cay,tahole tar upor click korle i hobe: <abbr title="HyperTextMarkupLanguage>HTML</abbr>

Address dekhate: <address>wonderful house,
Mirpur,dhaka-1200</address>

HTML e Comment korte: <!--        -->
HTML Color korte:
<h1 style="color:#ff0000;">ZAYED</h1>                <!-- #ff0000:eta red Hex color code -->
Or,
<h1 style="color:rgb(255,0,0);"> ZAYED </h1> <!-- rgb(255,0,0); :Eta red er rgb colorcode-->

Boarder color:
<h1 style="border: 2px solid rgb(233,226,205);"> ZAYED </h1>  

page er tilte site e dekhate: title ja likhben tai dekhabe. <title>ZAYEDS WEB</title>

lekhar font size boro korte:
<style>
h1
{
font-size:100px;
} 
</style>

* page e link set korte ja click korle oi page e web e niye jabe:
<a href="http://www.google.com/">Google</a>
*jodi ami cai noton arekta tab open hoye noton website e jak,tahole:
<a href="http://www.google.com/"target="_blank">Google</a>
tokon ei Google lekhar niche underline dekhabe, eta ke dekhanor jonno:text-decoration:underline dewa jay,
underline chara Google lekhati page e show korte:text-decoration:none ditee hobe.

*PNG image e:kono logo r background takena,background chara add kora jabe,
*JPG image e:kono logo add korle kothaw tar attached background shoho add hoye jabe.
*gif image e:akta image ke animatory akare dekhabe.
Image add korar tag:<img src"google.jpg"alt="google logo"> ekhane src te image file er name likhte hobe,r 'alt'Attribute e sei image somporke otirikto information ta dewa thakee.

#Fevicon in HTML:eita add korle noton open howa web page e href e je image ta takbe seta title er pashe show korbe icon er moto.eta joss akta design.
<link rel="icon"type="image/x-icon"href="google.png">

#table make in HTML:
<table>
<tr> ...table row,
<th>Name</th> ...table heading. 
<th>Language</th>
<th>Year</th>
</tr>
</table>
table styling:
table{
font-family:"Courier New",Courier,nonospace;
border-collapse:collapse; ...eta dilee table er protiti column er bordar aladavave na dekhiye aksathe draw kora akta table er moto kore dekhabe.

#list in HTML:

1)<ul>:eti dara unordered list bujay.(circular,triangular,rectangular,square,disc,none....)
ex:
ul{
list-style-type:square;
}...eti dile icon golo square shape hobe.

2)<ol>:eti dara ordered list bojay.(1,2,3....)
ex:
<ol type="1"
<li>HTML</li>
<li>CSS</li>
<li>JS</li> egolo 1,2,3....evave dekhabe.

#Block element and Inline Block element:
*Block element holo:h1 tags and paragrap(<p>)tag,<address>,<aside>,<div>,<dl>,<dt>,<table>,<ul>,<vedio> etc.jara kono text borabor er proyojon er bairee o poraline ta block/box kore felbe.

*Inline element holo:<span>,<strong> tags,<i>,<img>,<b>,<button>,<sub>,<sup>,<em> etc.jara kono text borabor er proyojon jototoko sudu oitoko block/box korbe.

ol{
}
h1,
p,
span,
strong{
border:1px solid re;
}
***'Nu HTML Checker'website e kono HTML code e error ache kina seta check kora jay,copy past koree.

#HTML CLASS & HTML ID:
(akoi name doita id hote parbe na, id name e space takte parben na,underscore/hypen takte pare.kinto akadik class takte paree)Id select korar jonno amra dibo hash(#),r class select korar jonno amra dibo dot(.)

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>
        HTML CLASS & HTML ID
    </title>
</head>
<body>
#title{
background:red;
color:#fff
padding:10px.
.title{
font-family:"courier New",courier,nonospace;
}
.font-size{
font-size:20px;
}   <!..title class doijaigai thakai font family doijaigai i change hoyeche..>
</body>
</html>

#Iframe in HTML:
ja google map and youtube dekhate caile use hoy.
*News link er iframe tag:

<iframe src="https://www.protomalo.com/"width="600" height="600"></iframe>

** Youtube vedio er iframe tag:

<iframe width="300" height="200" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/u31qwQUeGuM"title="placeholder video"frameborder="0"allow="accelerometer;autoplay;
clipboard-write;encrypted-media;gyroscope;picture-in-picture"allowfullscreen></iframe>

** Google Map link er iframe tag:

<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d58403.623580890235!2d90.32726108274684!3d23.810544423860303!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13."width="300"height="200"style="border:0;"allowfullscreen=""loading="lazy"referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>

#JAVASCRIPT IN HTML:
<script>
alert("Hi! JavaScript"); ...erokom akta alert asbe.
</script> tag er bitor apni javascript use korte parben.

#File paths in HTML:
<img src="img/google.jpg" alt="">
or
<scipt src="js/app.js"></script>

ak file theke arek file er jinis use korte agee ber hote hobe,tar jonno dite (../),tar por ak file theke bairer arek file er jinis use kora jabe.

<img src="../googles.gif"alt="">

